				<td colspan="2"><span>I have heard so many rumours and ideas surrounding EQII that I don't have a clue what to expect. For one, I heard that KSing is going to be almost impossible, which is good. I've also read that soloing will also almost be impossible, and if doable, for a fraction of the XP. Of course one thing i haven't heard was even a hint of a release date. 
<br />

<br />
I love reading up on this kinda stuff so any info or subjects of controversy surrounding EQII would be great would be great to post here! <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
